# =============================================================
#  Retail Pricing Feed — .gitignore
#  Covers: .NET 8, Node/React, Docker, IDEs, OS artefacts
# =============================================================

# ── Operating System ─────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── .NET / C# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

## Visual Studio artefacts
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
.vs/
*.vspscc
*.vssscc

## Rider / JetBrains
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## Publish / deploy output
[Pp]ublish/
publish/
PublishProfiles/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## Entity Framework migrations temp files
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.ndf

## Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.VisualState.xml
TestResult.xml
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage.cobertura.xml
lcov.info

## Resharper
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

## dotCover
*.dotCover

## dotMemory
*.dmw

## dotTrace
*.dtp

## BenchmarkDotNet
BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/

# ── Node.js / React / Microfrontends ─────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

## Build output
dist/
dist-ssr/
build/
.next/
out/

## Parcel
.cache/
.parcel-cache/

## Webpack Module Federation remote manifests (runtime-generated)
remoteEntry.js

## Vite
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*

## TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

## Environment / secrets
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local
.env.*.local

## Package manager locks (keep package-lock.json or yarn.lock but not both)
# Uncomment the one you DON'T use:
# package-lock.json
# yarn.lock
# pnpm-lock.yaml

## Coverage
coverage/
lcov.info
.nyc_output/

# ── Docker ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Ignore locally-generated compose overrides and bind-mount data
docker-compose.override.yml
.docker/
docker-data/

# ── Secrets & Configuration ───────────────────────────────────
## Never commit real connection strings or keys
appsettings.Production.json
appsettings.Staging.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.pem
*.cer
*.crt

## Azure / AWS credential files
.azure/
.aws/
local.settings.json

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.log.*
logs/
log/

# ── Editors ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## VS Code (keep shared workspace settings, ignore personal ones)
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

## Vim / Emacs
*~
*.swp
*.swo
[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]
[._]*.sw[a-p]
Session.vim
.netrwhist
tags

# ── Temporary & misc ─────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.orig
*.rej
*.patch
*.diff
*.cache
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# ── Claude ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
